packages.packageDescription:
Life's as big as you make it in an Atlas, and you can make it huge with the Tow Hitch Package. Its 5,000-lb. towing capacity* helps you bring along your favorite recreational toy on weekend getaways and vacations. So hitch things up, pick a spot, and let the adventures begin.

The Tow Hitch Package includes:
  • Tow hitch

*Maximum tow rating when equipped with V6 engine and factory installed towing hitch. Vehicle load, other accessories and options may reduce maximum towing capacity. See vehicle owner’s manual for details.

Two separate chairs for the 2nd row give each passenger the comfort and space of their very own seat. Each back and arm rest is adjustable, and the chairs can slide for extra legroom. Even with a child seat attached, 3rd-row access is still a breeze, and the seat backs can fold flat for maximum cargo space.

The 2nd-row Captain's Chairs Package includes:
  • 2nd-row Captain's chairs with 3rd-row easy entry
2nd-row Captain's chairs reduces total seating capacity to six. Always ensure that child restraint system is securely attached to vehicle.

We've made the Premium even more premium with this special R-Line appearance package. Bold, sporty touches like 20" alloy wheels and R-Line bumpers give the Tiguan a sportier look on the outside. Inside, the same impression is enhanced by a stainless steel footrest and pedal covers and R-line door sill plates.

The SEL Premium R-Line Package includes:

  • 20" alloy wheels
  • R-Line bumpers
  • Stainless steel footrest and pedal covers
  • Scuff plates on door sills
